""" Get an HDF5 file's group list """
filename, fid = hdf_dataset
grp_list = get_groups(fid)
assert set(grp_list) == {'/', 'Group1', 'Group2', 'Group2/Group3', 'Group4',
    'Group4/Group5', 'Group4/Group5/Group6'}
grp_list = get_groups(filename)
assert set(grp_list) == {'/', 'Group1', 'Group2', 'Group2/Group3', 'Group4',
    'Group4/Group5', 'Group4/Group5/Group6'}
